trans-unit.source: Defines a set of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref> fields that each correspond to a command function provided by the host environment.
trans-unit.target: 定義一組<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID"></xref>欄位每個對應至主機環境所提供的命令函式。

trans-unit.source: MenuCommands contains a set of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> fields that can be used to specify a command to link when adding a command using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.
trans-unit.target: MenuCommands 包含一組<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>欄位，可以用來指定要將連結加入命令，使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A><xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>方法</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A>時的命令</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID>
